<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.10.9">
<l>vañcaṉaiyāl vantavaḷta ṉuyiruṇṭu vāytta tayiruṇṭu veṇṇeyamu tuṇṭuvali mikka</l>
<l>kañcaṉuyi ratuvuṇṭiv vulakuṇṭa kāḷai karutumiṭaṅ kāvirican takilkaṉaka munti</l>
<l>mañculavu poḻilūṭum vayalūṭum vantu vaḷaṅkoṭuppa māmaṟaiyōr māmalarkaḷ tūvi</l>
<l>añcalittaṅ karicaraṇeṉ ṟiraiñcumaṇi nāṅkū rarimēya viṇṇakaram vaṇaṅkumaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Simple heart, worship in Arimēya Viṇṇakaram in lovely Nānkūr</l>
<l rend="indent">where great Vedic experts bow, scattering huge blossoms, joining palms,</l>
<l>And chanting, “Hari [is our] refuge,” as the Kāviri grants bounty,</l>
<l rend="indent">coming through fields and through groves where mist drifts,</l>
<l>Casting up sandal [wood], aquila [wood], and gold, the place where is manifest</l>
<l rend="indent">the youth who, having consumed the life of her who came in deceit,</l>
<l>Having consumed the collected curds, consumed ghee [and] milk,</l>
<l rend="indent">and consumed the life of Kaṁsa of great strength,</l>
<l rend="indent">consumed this [entire] world.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
